      "text": "{user}さん、ちょうどいいところに！\nエールトゥインクル～くるくるぽーん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}‚ just in time!\nAle Twinkle~ Twirl‚ twirl‚ pon!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "え、エールトゥインクル……？\nどうしたんだ急に……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A-Ale Twinkle…?\nWhat's with you all of a sudden…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.5666667699
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "すみません……まだ修行が足りないみたいです\nまた出直してきます～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry… I guess my training is still lacking.\nI'll go and start over~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.8666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4733.333230100001,
          "startTime": 24.3
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "―― A few hours later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.8578124602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
