      "text": "{user}さん！　今度こそ！\nトリニティトリトリ～ぱたぱたぴょーん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}! This time for sure!\nTrinity Tri-Tri~ Flap‚ flap‚ pyon!",
        "id": ""
      },
