      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（……はっ！　もしかしてすみれ、俺に魔法を）\n（かけているつもりなのか！？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…Wait! Is she trying to cast a spell）\n（on me!?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.2666677872
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ううっ！　な、なんて強力な魔法なんだ……！\nやられた……ガクッ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh! S-Such powerful magic…!\nYou got me… collapse",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.4666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5633.332212799999,
          "startTime": 53.9
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.8666677872
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんなんで倒れてるんですか！？\n今のは仕事の疲れを癒す魔法だったんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}‚ why are you falling down!?\nThat was supposed to be a spell to heal your work fatigue…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "えっ……！？　あ、あー、なんだか体が\n軽くなった気がするぞぉー？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh…!? O-Oh‚ somehow my body\nfeels lighter now—?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.2000011205
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "んん～？　なんだか嘘くさいですね……\nかくなる上は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm~? That sounds a bit suspicious…\nIn that case…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 76.1333344538
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "ウニャミュチュペギューリュ……破ーっ！\nウニャミュチュペギューリュ……破ーっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Unya-myu-chu-pegyu-ryu… Ha!\nUnya-myu-chu-pegyu-ryu… Ha!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.9000011205
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみれ？　それは俺に呪いをかけてるのか？\n怖いからやめて欲しいんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sumire? Are you putting a curse on me?\nIt's scary‚ so please stop…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 90.9333344538
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "すみません、{user}さん……\n本当は、疲れを癒してあげたかったんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ {user}…\nActually‚ I just wanted to heal your fatigue…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "それにしては、凄い形相だったが……じゃなくて\nすみれ、さっきから変だぞ？　何かあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You had a pretty terrifying look for that… but anyway‚\nSumire‚ you've been strange for a while. Did something happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 105.8333344538
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "実は……この間選ばれた『どきドキ♡ラブコメ\nファンタジー』の魔法少女役で悩んでいて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To be honest… I've been worried about the \"Doki Doki♡\nRom-com Fantasy\" magical girl role…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.6333344538
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "台本は、他のみんなの分のセリフも全部覚えたんです\nでも……魔法だけが、魔法だけが習得出来なくて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've even memorized everyone else's lines in the script.\nBut… magic‚ only the magic‚ I just can't master it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 126.5333344538
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "毎日、寝る間も惜しんで詠唱の練習をしたり\n空を飛ぶ練習もしてるのに……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I spend every day practicing incantations instead of sleeping‚\nand even practicing how to fly…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（これはかなり重症だな……なんとかしないと）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（This is a serious case… I have to do something.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.3000011205,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.8000011205
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "俺はすみれが自然体で演じたらそれでいいと\n思うんだが……それが難しいんだよな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think it's enough if you just act naturally‚\nSumire… but that's the hard part‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 139.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "はい。頭では分かってるんですけど、ファンのみんなの\n期待に応えなくちゃって考えるほど迷走しちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I know it in my head‚ but the more I think\nabout meeting fans' expectations‚ the more I get lost…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.1333344538
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_12_02-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "何度挑戦しても、いくら修行を積んでも\nふわふわマジカルウィングが出ないんです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No matter how many times I try or how much I train‚\nmy \"Fluffy Magical Wings\" won't appear!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
